{"tid":251161,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[選擇困難]兩部錢七邊架好","createTime":"2017-05-20T16:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T13:47:27.000Z","uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec086a08c545a912aca9e274a16a48b3e3c4f99a","tid":251161,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"講明先只係兩萬左右錢七，但新手未買過車驚中伏<br />\n所以上黎問下<br />\n<br />\n兩架都係豐田，一樣年份一樣款<br />\n<br />\nA: 車房d車黎(非相熟車房)，牌費長<br />\n個殼唔靚，花花地<br />\n<br />\nB: 應該係私人賣，個殼少花,幾企理，牌費幾個月<br />\n<br />\n價錢就兩架都一樣，比你會點揀?<br />\n殼靚同機件保養應該無必然關係?<br />\n車房車會唔會易d中伏?<br />\n<br />\n最驚買返黎要經常整，果兩蚊野分分鐘整到比個double<br />\n又要煩，到整又驚比人水魚<br />\n<br />\n巴打指點下小弟thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c712198f8dec3100d5fbb59dfa0a2f12fbe02f49","tid":251161,"uid":40796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:18:49.000Z","msg":"Plan A 㗎車花成點先 如果唔係好嚴重<br />\n打蠟都可以搞番掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a58ad08e797667094f22525c166d2a37590b62","tid":251161,"uid":50818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"我會考慮B果部先"},{"pid":"5b012c93428bed48c4857964d66a227d29e4812e","tid":251161,"uid":1715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"車行啲車收到平一平賣就賣到貴一貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8e5da8a2bd76985260d5cf5d643a619599674f","tid":251161,"uid":52542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"第一架車10k私人放<br />\n但上手唔識照顧份偈漏油漏到m come咁<br />\n前手隊頭隊尾，泵把唔對位，無入陣<br />\n<br />\n第二架trade in 車黎，6000蚊，上過架細執<br />\n機器精神，但個尾都隊過無入陣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔急可以睇多幾架，或者上架，一清二楚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f562d478646003f0ceb2b